fgeo 1.1.2 (GitHub and drat)

This document records developer-facing changes (users: see NEWS.md).

  • Builds on Travis CI are now tested on Windows, Mac, and Linux, and from R-devel to R 3.2 (see cran-comments.md).

  • The website now builds automatically and deploys on the gh-branch.

  • Automated builds of all fgeo packages can now be tracked not only on Travis CI but also on to the #fgeo-builds channel of ForestGEO’s slack workspace (request an invitation).

Thanks to the reviewers!

Developed by Mauro Lepore, Gabriel Arellano, Richard Condit, Stuart Davies, Matteo Detto, Erika Gonzalez-Akre, Pamela Hall, Kyle Harms, Valentine Herrmann, Aaron Hogan, Bier Kraichak, David Kenfack, Suzanne Lao, Sean McMahon, Sabrina Russo, Cara Scalpone, Kristina Teixeira, Graham Zemunik, Daniel Zuleta, CTFS-ForestGEO.
